WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:03.590
Good morning, family. Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:05.670
Thank you for joining us again today.

00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:07.670
Well, I have my sweetheart here with me,

00:00:07.680 --> 00:00:09.350
and I told her I wanted her to

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:11.030
say something at the very beginning.

00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:12.629
Yes. Good morning.

00:00:12.639 --> 00:00:13.350
Good morning.

00:00:13.360 --> 00:00:14.789
Thank you so much.

00:00:14.799 --> 00:00:18.550
Yeah. I seem

