home, saying, 'God doesn't take care

00:32:56.640 --> 00:32:57.990
of us,'and just popping off. He said,

00:32:58.000 --> 00:32:59.190
'Shut up, or I'm going to hit you in the head,'basically, because

00:32:59.190 --> 00:32:59.200
God is

00:32:59.200 --> 00:33:00.870
going to

00:33:00.880 --> 00:33:03.830
take care of us. And so they got all the

00:33:03.840 --> 00:33:05.669
way home, and he was bickering back and

00:33:05.679 --> 00:33:07.430
forth, him and his brother, because they

00:33:07.440 --> 00:33:09.750
didn't have anything to eat. And all of a

00:33:09.760 --> 00:33:11.509
sudden,

00:33:11.509 --> 00:33:11.519
Mama—because

00:33:11.519 --> 00:33:12.870
Mama said, 'I'm not going to beg for

00:33:12.880 --> 00:33:13.990
money. We're not going to do

00:33:13.990 --> 00:33:14.000
anything'—well,

00:33:14.000 --> 00:33:15.590
they got invited over to the

00:33:15.600 --> 00:33:17.669
neighbor's house, and she had all that

00:33:17.679 --> 00:33:20.149
food set out, remember? And they

00:33:20.159 --> 00:33:22.950
saw them eating the food, and

00:33:22.950 --> 00:33:22.960
Mama

00:33:22.960 --> 00:33:24.710
said, 'No, we're

00:33:24.710 --> 00:33:24.720
fine.'And

00:33:24.720 --> 00:33:26.470
he was

00:33:26.480 --> 00:33:27.590
thinking, 'No, we're not! We're

00:33:28.389 --> 00:33:28.399
starving!'They

00:33:29.840 --> 00:33:31.750
sat there and watched them

00:33:32.159 --> 00:33:33.509
because they said, 'Do you want to

00:33:33.519 --> 00:33:34.870
eat some of this?'and she

00:33:34.880 --> 00:33:36.710
said, 'No, we're okay. We're going to be

00:33:36.720 --> 00:33:37.909
just fine. God's going to take care of

00:33:37.909 --> 00:33:37.919
us.'So

00:33:37.919 --> 00:33:41.830
they went home,

00:33:41.840 --> 00:33:44.549
and what happened? Something hit their

00:33:44.559 --> 00:33:45.990
door.

00:33:46.000 --> 00:33:48.789
Somebody knocked

00:33:48.799 --> 00:33:50.630
on their door, and when they

00:33:50.640 --> 00:33:52.950
opened the door, there was all this

00:33:52.950 --> 00:33:52.960
food—all

00:33:52.960 --> 00:33:54.470
these groceries.

00:33:55.120 --> 00:33:56.710
There was a

00:33:56.720 --> 00:33:59.269
full turkey, gravy,

00:33:59.279 --> 00:34:00.070
biscuits—and

00:34:00.080 --> 00:34:02.389
it

00:34:02.399 --> 00:34:04.870
was

00:34:04.880 --> 00:34:06.549
at night. It

00:34:06.549 --> 00:34:06.559
was

00:34:06.559 --> 00:34:09.030
at night, and he said

00:34:09.040 --> 00:34:10.869
Mom went in there, and they were so

00:34:10.879 --> 00:34:13.349
hungry she made a

00:34:13.349 --> 00:34:13.359
big feast.

00:34:13.359 --> 00:34:15.510
She goes, 'Oral, go get the flour.'She got a big sack of flour,

00:34:15.520 --> 00:34:17.270
she got the

00:34:17.280 --> 00:34:19.109
eggs, and she said, 'Oral, go get the

00:34:19.119 --> 00:34:20.149
stuff out there. I'm going to make

00:34:20.159 --> 00:34:22.230
something to eat.'So they made it

00:34:22.240 --> 00:34:25.510
at night. They had a huge feast of

00:34:25.520 --> 00:34:27.190
biscuits and gravy, and they went to bed.

00:34:27.200 --> 00:34:28.950
And he told his little brother,

00:34:28.960 --> 00:34:31.109
'I told you God would provide

00:34:31.119 --> 00:34:32.389
for us.

00:34:32.399 --> 00:34:34.550
I told you God would provide for

00:34:34.550 --> 00:34:34.560
us.'And

00:34:34.560 --> 00:34:36.869
every time I hear that,

00:34:36.869 --> 00:34:36.879
I say,

00:34:36.879 --> 00:34:39.829
'He'll do it again and again.

00:34:39.839 --> 00:34:41.990
He'll do it again and again if you

00:34:42.000 --> 00:34:44.869
believe Him.'I'm a believing believer.

00:34:44.879 --> 00:34:47.270
I'm not a doubter. And I tell you

00:34:47.280 --> 00:34:49.829
these stories of what God is doing

00:34:49.839 --> 00:34:51.990
to inspire you to believe for your

00:34:52.000 --> 00:34:53.829
family in the days ahead, to say, 'Hey,

00:34:53.839 --> 00:34:56.149
I'm not going to participate in

00:34:56.149 --> 00:34:56.159
this.'I

00:34:56.159 --> 00:34:58.069
know what the Lord has told me is

00:34:58.079 --> 00:35:00.310
coming, ladies and gentlemen. And it

00:35:00.320 --> 00:35:02.950
will be times like we've never seen

00:35:02.960 --> 00:35:05.829
before because back then in the 1930s,

00:35:05.839 --> 00:35:07.750
people at least knew how to grow a

00:35:07.760 --> 00:35:09.030
garden.

00:35:09.040 --> 00:35:11.589
Now they don't even know how to

00:35:11.599 --> 00:35:13.910
grow some flowers,

00:35:13.920 --> 00:35:17.270
let alone a garden. It's serious. And so

00:35:17.280 --> 00:35:19.030
that's what the Lord was showing me:

00:35:19.040 --> 00:35:20.550
people don't even know how to hunt. What

00:35:20.560 --> 00:35:21.670
would you do if you shot an animal? They

00:35:21.680 --> 00:35:23.430
don't know how to even gut an animal,

00:35:23.440 --> 00:35:25.510
field dress it, and get it cleaned up.

00:35:25.520 --> 00:35:27.510
They wouldn't know what to do.

00:35:27.520 --> 00:35:28.790
That's what I'm saying. There's a lot of people

00:35:28.790 --> 00:35:28.800
who are

00:35:28.800 --> 00:35:30.710
not educated. They know

00:35:30.720 --> 00:35:32.150
a lot about computers, but they don't

00:35:32.160 --> 00:35:34.150
know about how to live. They know how to

00:35:34.160 --> 00:35:35.910
go down to McDonald's and tell them,

00:35:35.920 --> 00:35:37.670
'I want a Happy Meal,'but they don't know

00:35:37.680 --> 00:35:40.790
how to do this. And I've seen very

00:35:40.800 --> 00:35:44.390
challenging days in the near future when

00:35:44.400 --> 00:35:46.150
this plague comes and these

00:35:46.160 --> 00:35:48.069
times come. There are hard times I've seen

00:35:48.079 --> 00:35:50.550
coming. Now, can we pray? People

00:35:50.550 --> 00:35:50.560
say

00:35:50.560 --> 00:35:53.109
that's the main thing: 'Can we pray

00:35:53.119 --> 00:35:55.990
this

00:35:55.990 --> 00:35:56.000
away?'I

00:35:56.000 --> 00:35:59.190
know that God can lessen anything,

00:35:59.200 --> 00:36:01.349
but there are parts of it... we don't

00:36:01.359 --> 00:36:04.470
want to go through hard times because we

00:36:04.480 --> 00:36:07.270
want to pass it on to the next person.

00:36:07.280 --> 00:36:09.990
But what will shake the world to

00:36:10.000 --> 00:36:11.510
bring in the harvest? That's why I said

00:36:11.510 --> 00:36:11.520
that

00:36:11.520 --> 00:36:12.950
whenever Jesus was

00:36:12.960 --> 00:36:14.150
getting ready to die on the cross, he

00:36:14.160 --> 00:36:17.670
said, 'Not my will, but yours be

00:36:17.670 --> 00:36:17.680
done.'It's

00:36:17.680 --> 00:36:20.950
not always comfortable for my flesh

00:36:20.960 --> 00:36:23.510
to go through something sometimes.

00:36:23.510 --> 00:36:23.520
Yea,

00:36:23.520 --> 00:36:25.109
though I walk through the valley of the

00:36:25.119 --> 00:36:27.109
shadow of death, I will fear no evil. He

00:36:27.119 --> 00:36:28.310
didn't say you wouldn't walk through the

00:36:28.320 --> 00:36:29.990
valley.

00:36:30.000 --> 00:36:31.670
Sometimes you walk through the valley,

00:36:31.680 --> 00:36:34.710
but we don't have to fear it.

00:36:34.720 --> 00:36:37.670
Sometimes we go through, you know,

00:36:37.680 --> 00:36:39.190
'A thousand shall fall at our side, ten thousand

00:36:39.190 --> 00:36:39.200
at our

00:36:39.200 --> 00:36:40.950
right hand.'That means there are

00:36:40.960 --> 00:36:43.829
people dying around you. Regardless

00:36:43.839 --> 00:36:45.910
if a thousand fell around you or ten thousand

00:36:45.910 --> 00:36:45.920
at your

00:36:45.920 --> 00:36:48.310
right hand, something's going on for

00:36:48.320 --> 00:36:50.710
that to be happening. That means

00:36:50.720 --> 00:36:51.990
something was happening. Do you

00:36:52.000 --> 00:36:54.790
understand? Ten thousand, am I right?

00:36:54.790 --> 00:36:54.800
Ten

00:36:54.800 --> 00:36:56.630
thousand. I mean, seriously,

00:36:56.640 --> 00:36:58.710
that's a lot of folks. That's 11,000

00:36:58.720 --> 00:37:00.550
people.

00:37:00.560 --> 00:37:03.270
That's a bad day.

00:37:03.280 --> 00:37:06.390
But it won't come nigh me. 'Only with thine

00:37:06.390 --> 00:37:06.400
eyes

00:37:06.400 --> 00:37:08.150
shalt thou behold and see the reward of

00:37:08.160 --> 00:37:10.550
the

00:37:10.550 --> 00:37:10.560
wicked.'Father,

00:37:10.560 --> 00:37:13.030
I thank you, Lord, for

00:37:13.030 --> 00:37:13.040
Psalm

00:37:13.040 --> 00:37:14.950
91. But even in the midst of

00:37:14.950 --> 00:37:14.960
Psalm

00:37:14.960 --> 00:37:17.670
91, and us quoting that and

00:37:17.680 --> 00:37:19.510
believing that, there's a lot of stuff

00:37:19.520 --> 00:37:23.510
going on around us as we're saying that.

00:37:23.520 --> 00:37:25.349
It's saying that we're still protected,

00:37:25.359 --> 00:37:26.870
but man, there's still something going

00:37:26.880 --> 00:37:31.030
on. And people need to understand

00:37:31.040 --> 00:37:33.829
trying times come, but we stand by our

00:37:33.839 --> 00:37:36.390
covenant rights and we say, 'Fill the

00:37:36.400 --> 00:37:40.390
pot up, Lord. Fill the pot up, Lord. I

00:37:40.400 --> 00:37:42.390
don't want beans, Lord. I thank you,

00:37:42.400 --> 00:37:44.069
Lord. Whatever you provide for me, Lord,

00:37:44.079 --> 00:37:46.230
I'm grateful for. But Lord, my faith's out

00:37:46.240 --> 00:37:48.550
there for some

00:37:48.560 --> 00:37:51.990
chicken noodles.'I mean, I don't know. I

00:37:52.000 --> 00:37:53.829
just want you to learn how to

00:37:53.839 --> 00:37:57.589
believe God where you are right now.

00:37:57.599 --> 00:37:59.750
Believe God for where you are right now

00:37:59.760 --> 00:38:01.990
and exercise your faith right now for

00:38:02.000 --> 00:38:03.510
something.

00:38:03.520 --> 00:38:06.950
Use your faith for something small and

00:38:06.960 --> 00:38:09.990
believe God for it. For when hard, trying

00:38:10.000 --> 00:38:15.510
times come, you won't faint.

00:38:15.520 --> 00:38:17.670
This won't take you over.

00:38:17.680 --> 00:38:18.630
You practice now

00:38:18.640 --> 00:38:21.430
because you practice while times are good

00:38:21.440 --> 00:38:23.990
and there's plenty, so that you don't

00:38:24.000 --> 00:38:25.990
freak out when things are a

00:38:26.000 --> 00:38:28.870
little shaky and you go, 'Oh, no.

00:38:28.870 --> 00:38:28.880
No.'There's

00:38:28.880 --> 00:38:31.030
no 'Oh, no.'We're good.

00:38:31.040 --> 00:38:33.349
God is good in the good times and God

00:38:33.349 --> 00:38:33.359
is

00:38:33.359 --> 00:38:35.910
good in the bad times. God is good

00:38:35.920 --> 00:38:37.349
on the mountain and he's good in the

00:38:37.359 --> 00:38:38.550
valley.

00:38:38.560 --> 00:38:41.430
God is faithful. He is able and he will

00:38:41.440 --> 00:38:44.230
do what he promised us he would do if we

00:38:44.240 --> 00:38:46.390
believe him for it. But you need to

00:38:46.400 --> 00:38:48.310
learn how to believe him now in the good

00:38:48.320 --> 00:38:51.030
times instead of

00:38:51.030 --> 00:38:51.040
saying

00:38:51.040 --> 00:38:52.230
we're going to wait until

00:38:52.240 --> 00:38:54.550
when the times are bad. That's what I'm

00:38:54.560 --> 00:38:56.710
trying to tell you all. You need to put

00:38:56.720 --> 00:39:00.069
your boat into motion now.

00:39:00.079 --> 00:39:01.829
If you can't believe him for a dollar

00:39:01.839 --> 00:39:03.589
now, what makes you think you're

00:39:03.599 --> 00:39:04.630
going to be able to believe him for

00:39:04.640 --> 00:39:09.109
$100 later? You must start somewhere.

00:39:09.119 --> 00:39:11.349
Believe God and write your list

00:39:11.359 --> 00:39:13.589
down and tithe and give and

00:39:13.599 --> 00:39:15.430
show God that you're serious about him

00:39:15.440 --> 00:39:17.670
and be all in. Don't say, 'Well, when

00:39:17.680 --> 00:39:20.710
times get bad, Lord, here I am.

00:39:20.720 --> 00:39:21.990
You know, I just want to let you know,

00:39:22.000 --> 00:39:23.990
Lord, I'm on your

00:39:23.990 --> 00:39:24.000
side.'Whenever

00:39:24.000 --> 00:39:26.950
you see everybody dying around you, I'm

00:39:26.960 --> 00:39:30.470
all in before the storm comes.

00:39:30.480 --> 00:39:34.150
I'm not a fair-weather Christian. When

00:39:34.160 --> 00:39:36.390
times are good, I'm out

00:39:36.400 --> 00:39:38.550
partying. But when times are bad, a

00:39:38.560 --> 00:39:40.550
thousand fall at my side, ten thousand at my

00:39:40.550 --> 00:39:40.560
right

00:39:40.560 --> 00:39:42.790
hand, 'We better pray and take communion,

00:39:42.800 --> 00:39:44.310
honey.'Seriously,

00:39:44.320 --> 00:39:46.790
I'm not that way with God.

00:39:46.800 --> 00:39:50.310
I told God, 'I want you

00:39:50.320 --> 00:39:53.030
to know, man, you search me and know me.

00:39:53.040 --> 00:39:55.109
You know my heart. I'm not rotten at the

00:39:55.119 --> 00:39:57.510
core. I may have a bad day, but I don't

00:39:57.520 --> 00:40:00.310
stay in that bad day.'I don't stay in

00:40:00.320 --> 00:40:05.030
the bad day. I choose to follow Jesus

00:40:05.040 --> 00:40:08.470
in good and in bad, on the mountain or in

00:40:08.480 --> 00:40:11.430
the valley. Do you understand? God's

00:40:11.440 --> 00:40:13.270
still God, and he's God on the mountain

00:40:13.280 --> 00:40:15.030
and he's God in the valley. I love that

00:40:15.040 --> 00:40:17.829
song.

00:40:17.839 --> 00:40:20.710
But I just want you to know, when I see

00:40:20.720 --> 00:40:23.510
all these things, I'm just trying to

00:40:23.520 --> 00:40:25.589
be obedient to what the

00:40:25.599 --> 00:40:28.950
Lord has told me to say.

00:40:28.960 --> 00:40:30.950
And I know it's not always

00:40:30.960 --> 00:40:32.950
popular, but I appreciate you all

00:40:32.960 --> 00:40:34.790
listening because it's for your own

00:40:34.800 --> 00:40:36.390
good. But that's what I try to tell

00:40:36.400 --> 00:40:37.910
Dino. What is it going to take to get

00:40:37.920 --> 00:40:39.910
the revival?

00:40:39.920 --> 00:40:42.870
Where are we at with it? Praying into it

00:40:42.880 --> 00:40:45.030
and asking God to do something

00:40:45.040 --> 00:40:47.829
supernatural in these last days. But

00:40:47.839 --> 00:40:50.710
when I see all the things I see and they

00:40:50.720 --> 00:40:53.670
all go together in some way, I just have

00:40:53.680 --> 00:40:55.510
an urgency

00:40:55.520 --> 00:40:57.829
in this window not to take it for

00:40:57.839 --> 00:41:00.069
granted. You don't

00:41:00.079 --> 00:41:03.190
squander the time. I want you to be

00:41:03.200 --> 00:41:05.910
serious about the times ahead.

00:41:05.920 --> 00:41:07.750
And people are like, 'Well,

00:41:07.760 --> 00:41:09.829
how many, Brandon?

00:41:09.839 --> 00:41:12.390
Is that the tribulation you're

00:41:12.390 --> 00:41:12.400
seeing?'No,

00:41:12.400 --> 00:41:16.950
it's not the tribulation I'm seeing.

00:41:16.960 --> 00:41:19.430
This is right before the tribulation.

00:41:19.440 --> 00:41:21.990
This is the beginning of sorrows, the

00:41:22.000 --> 00:41:25.510
great birthing pains. This is 'as the

00:41:25.520 --> 00:41:28.309
days of Noah, so will it be.'This is

00:41:28.319 --> 00:41:31.990
where we are and headed. And a

00:41:32.000 --> 00:41:34.069
lot of people do not realize how much we

00:41:34.079 --> 00:41:35.589
will see before the coming of the Lord

00:41:35.599 --> 00:41:38.630
Jesus Christ. I believe you. That's why

00:41:38.640 --> 00:41:40.790
I try to tell people, you have no idea

00:41:40.800 --> 00:41:42.870
how bad tribulation is truly going to

00:41:42.880 --> 00:41:44.790
be.

00:41:44.800 --> 00:41:48.550
It's going to be literal hell on earth.

00:41:48.560 --> 00:41:50.790
When I went to tribulation with the Lord

00:41:50.800 --> 00:41:54.470
on July 6th of 2014, it was

00:41:54.480 --> 00:41:56.230
something that shook me for the rest of

00:41:56.240 --> 00:41:59.670
my life. I had glimpses of it. And I

00:41:59.680 --> 00:42:03.589
walked with Jesus through tribulation.

00:42:03.599 --> 00:42:08.550
And I can tell you, folks,

00:42:08.560 --> 00:42:10.790
that

00:42:10.800 --> 00:42:13.030
visitation that I had with the Lord

00:42:13.040 --> 00:42:16.150
forever changed me. I can't get it out

00:42:16.160 --> 00:42:18.870
of my memory. It

00:42:18.870 --> 00:42:18.880
was as

00:42:18.880 --> 00:42:21.190
real as me touching my wife right

00:42:21.200 --> 00:42:23.270
now.

00:42:23.280 --> 00:42:26.390
And I'm telling you, no one knows how

00:42:26.400 --> 00:42:28.470
bad it truly is going to be in the

00:42:28.480 --> 00:42:31.030
tribulation. You go, 'Well, you know,

00:42:31.040 --> 00:42:32.710
no, no, no. If the days weren't

00:42:32.720 --> 00:42:35.670
shortened, no man would survive

00:42:35.670 --> 00:42:35.680
it.'He's

00:42:35.680 --> 00:42:38.230
going to have to shorten the time.

00:42:38.240 --> 00:42:39.829
I don't know what that means, but I'm

00:42:39.839 --> 00:42:42.550
telling you this: what I saw for the

00:42:42.560 --> 00:42:44.150
little glimpse that I saw of the

00:42:44.160 --> 00:42:46.390
Christians that were left here because

00:42:46.400 --> 00:42:48.309
they thought they were living right and

00:42:48.319 --> 00:42:49.990
they had compromised in their heart and

00:42:50.000 --> 00:42:51.990
they did not—they weren't sold

00:42:51.990 --> 00:42:52.000
out—and

00:42:52.000 --> 00:42:53.670
they were the virgins

00:42:53.670 --> 00:42:53.680
where

00:42:53.680 --> 00:42:57.270
five had their lamps full and five

00:42:57.280 --> 00:43:00.870
didn't. Half the Christians will be left

00:43:00.880 --> 00:43:03.510
and half will be taken. I'm telling you,

00:43:03.520 --> 00:43:07.430
I saw it. I was here. I watched them and

00:43:07.440 --> 00:43:09.270
they were scurrying around like a bunch

00:43:09.280 --> 00:43:12.790
of rats on a ship. It was terrible. How

00:43:12.800 --> 00:43:14.470
many people thought they were

00:43:14.470 --> 00:43:14.480
qualified

00:43:14.480 --> 00:43:15.990
and were ready for the

00:43:16.000 --> 00:43:17.349
rapture of the church, and they thought,

00:43:17.359 --> 00:43:19.190
'Man, I'm just out here

00:43:19.200 --> 00:43:20.790
living a party life, but I'm saved. I

00:43:20.800 --> 00:43:22.710
love the Lord.'But they had one foot in

00:43:22.720 --> 00:43:24.950
the world and one foot with Jesus.

00:43:24.960 --> 00:43:27.190
And I saw how many people were left.

00:43:27.200 --> 00:43:29.990
There were literally tens of thousands

00:43:30.000 --> 00:43:33.990
in just one area where I was at, and they

00:43:34.000 --> 00:43:36.950
were screaming and cussing and acting

00:43:36.960 --> 00:43:39.270
out because they were left and they knew

00:43:39.280 --> 00:43:42.150
what had happened and they weren't taken

00:43:42.160 --> 00:43:44.630
and they were mad and they were flipping

00:43:44.640 --> 00:43:46.710
the Lord off. They were doing all kinds

00:43:46.720 --> 00:43:48.069
of stuff. And that shows you where their

00:43:48.079 --> 00:43:49.510
heart was right there. They weren't

00:43:49.520 --> 00:43:51.430
falling on their knees and repenting.

00:43:51.440 --> 00:43:53.589
They were acting in anger and they saw

00:43:53.599 --> 00:43:56.150
their pastors that didn't preach the

00:43:56.160 --> 00:43:59.430
truth and they were ready to hang them.

00:43:59.440 --> 00:44:02.150
Kill them right there. I saw them. There

00:44:02.160 --> 00:44:04.790
was no Holy Ghost. The presence of the

00:44:04.800 --> 00:44:06.550
Lord, the prayer covering that the

00:44:06.560 --> 00:44:09.589
church had brought was gone.

00:44:09.599 --> 00:44:12.550
For the first time ever, you

00:44:12.560 --> 00:44:14.150
don't realize the prayer covering

00:44:14.160 --> 00:44:18.150
the church, the body of Christ, brings.

00:44:18.160 --> 00:44:21.670
The great restrainer—us, the church,

00:44:21.680 --> 00:44:23.349
the ones that are

00:44:23.359 --> 00:44:25.510
radical and on fire—were taken out of

00:44:25.520 --> 00:44:28.390
here. And for the first time ever, that

00:44:28.400 --> 00:44:30.150
prayer covering that was over the world

00:44:30.160 --> 00:44:32.150
that we bring every day when we do these

00:44:32.160 --> 00:44:33.910
videos and you pray in your own time,

00:44:33.920 --> 00:44:36.870
you bring a peace over the earth by your

00:44:36.880 --> 00:44:39.349
prayers.

00:44:39.359 --> 00:44:41.190
The prayers of the righteous

00:44:41.190 --> 00:44:41.200
availeth

00:44:41.200 --> 00:44:44.550
much.

00:44:44.560 --> 00:44:46.790
Remember this.

00:44:46.800 --> 00:44:48.550
Remember what I'm trying to tell you,

00:44:48.550 --> 00:44:48.560
because

00:44:48.560 --> 00:44:51.190
you still have a window of opportunity

00:44:51.200 --> 00:44:53.750
to get your heart right.

00:44:53.760 --> 00:44:57.190
I remember, and I was there, and each year

00:44:57.200 --> 00:44:58.950
the Lord took me into the years of

00:44:58.960 --> 00:45:01.910
tribulation of how bad it truly gets.

00:45:01.920 --> 00:45:04.150
And the further tribulation, the seven

00:45:04.150 --> 00:45:04.160
years—the

00:45:04.160 --> 00:45:06.069
first three and a half years

00:45:06.079 --> 00:45:09.750
was not that bad. It was terrible

00:45:09.760 --> 00:45:12.790
compared to where we are right now, but the last

00:45:12.800 --> 00:45:16.470
was unbearable.

00:45:16.480 --> 00:45:19.030
I'm talking bugs. There it was.

00:45:19.040 --> 00:45:21.910
It was awful. It looked like

00:45:21.920 --> 00:45:24.309
your worst movie you could

00:45:24.319 --> 00:45:26.150
ever think of, some kind of sci-fi, and it

00:45:26.160 --> 00:45:28.710
was like something out of that

00:45:28.720 --> 00:45:31.190
with hailstones falling out of the sky.

00:45:31.200 --> 00:45:32.870
It was awful. Do you

00:45:32.880 --> 00:45:35.670
understand? We're talking about... There was no

00:45:35.680 --> 00:45:38.230
moral law

00:45:38.230 --> 00:45:38.240
except

00:45:38.240 --> 00:45:40.069
what the Antichrist

00:45:40.079 --> 00:45:41.750
brought in to make people fear

00:45:41.760 --> 00:45:44.309
him and worship him. Everybody

00:45:44.309 --> 00:45:44.319
was

00:45:44.319 --> 00:45:47.030
acting crazy.

00:45:47.040 --> 00:45:48.710
And then when they got the chip, it

00:45:48.720 --> 00:45:51.670
made them

00:45:51.670 --> 00:45:51.680
calm.

00:45:51.680 --> 00:45:53.270
It brought a sense of peace over their

00:45:53.280 --> 00:45:55.910
minds.

00:45:55.920 --> 00:45:58.230
All of a sudden that chip comes, and they

00:45:58.240 --> 00:45:59.750
inject that chip inside of you in your

00:45:59.760 --> 00:46:01.510
forehead or your hand, and all of a

00:46:01.520 --> 00:46:03.190
sudden they go and they're like

00:46:03.200 --> 00:46:05.190
stone cold. They lose

00:46:05.200 --> 00:46:07.510
everything. I'll never forget it.

00:46:07.520 --> 00:46:08.950
But the people who were acting nuts,

00:46:08.960 --> 00:46:10.550
trying to pillage and stuff, the more

00:46:10.560 --> 00:46:12.309
they forced them with the drones flying

00:46:12.309 --> 00:46:12.319
in—they

00:46:12.319 --> 00:46:14.790
had drones everywhere and they

00:46:14.800 --> 00:46:16.150
watched and they let them have a chance.

00:46:16.160 --> 00:46:17.510
You take the mark, or get your head cut

00:46:17.520 --> 00:46:19.030
off. And they went and they just did it

00:46:19.040 --> 00:46:21.430
right there like a guillotine.

00:46:21.440 --> 00:46:24.950
And I saw it, and more people did not

00:46:24.960 --> 00:46:26.630
want to take that chip.

00:46:26.640 --> 00:46:28.470
When you took it, it made you a

00:46:28.480 --> 00:46:30.710
zombie. But the rioting and all

00:46:30.720 --> 00:46:34.309
the looting stopped

00:46:34.319 --> 00:46:35.750
because they had a chip in their hand

00:46:35.760 --> 00:46:37.109
and they had a chip in their forehead,

00:46:37.119 --> 00:46:39.349
and they became like

00:46:39.359 --> 00:46:41.349
a zombie,

00:46:41.359 --> 00:46:43.829
and all the looting and all the rioting

00:46:43.839 --> 00:46:46.550
and the murdering and all the craziness

00:46:46.560 --> 00:46:49.670
stopped. It did.

00:46:49.680 --> 00:46:52.790
He brought a sense of peace through a

00:46:52.790 --> 00:46:52.800
falseness

00:46:52.800 --> 00:46:54.550
through who he was, the

00:46:54.560 --> 00:46:57.109
Antichrist, over the earth. And he ruled

00:46:57.119 --> 00:47:00.390
from that place. And I watched it and

00:47:00.400 --> 00:47:02.230
everybody was like obeying

00:47:02.240 --> 00:47:07.430
little robots.

00:47:07.440 --> 00:47:09.349
But there were groups of people,

00:47:09.359 --> 00:47:12.069
pockets of people that were resistant.

00:47:12.079 --> 00:47:13.589
But they couldn't resist because

00:47:13.599 --> 00:47:16.630
the guns they had were like little

00:47:16.640 --> 00:47:19.430
things that just knocked them out cold.

00:47:19.430 --> 00:47:19.440
It

00:47:19.440 --> 00:47:22.790
wasn't like what you think.

00:47:22.800 --> 00:47:25.190
The drones told everything you

00:47:25.200 --> 00:47:28.390
did. There were drones always. The

00:47:28.400 --> 00:47:30.870
sky sounded like it was buzzing around,

00:47:30.880 --> 00:47:32.710
and everything was always alive in the

00:47:32.720 --> 00:47:35.510
sky by the thousands of drones—tens of

00:47:35.520 --> 00:47:37.270
thousands. And they're always flying.

00:47:37.280 --> 00:47:38.630
And people think, 'Well, we'll just get

00:47:38.640 --> 00:47:41.589
away from that.'Nobody is going to

00:47:41.599 --> 00:47:44.150
hide from what I saw coming.

00:47:44.160 --> 00:47:45.990
It's not like the movies they try to

00:47:46.000 --> 00:47:49.270
make of it. No, they dug in the side of

00:47:49.280 --> 00:47:51.589
hills, in the side of the Ozarks, and in

00:47:51.599 --> 00:47:53.589
the mountains trying to hide. But the

00:47:53.599 --> 00:47:55.750
winters were so bad because the weather

00:47:55.760 --> 00:47:58.230
was so bad, with things happening with

00:47:58.240 --> 00:48:01.109
the weather, you couldn't eat. They

00:48:01.119 --> 00:48:03.270
starved to death in the side of these

00:48:03.280 --> 00:48:05.670
mountains.

00:48:05.680 --> 00:48:07.750
They starved to death. There was no

00:48:07.760 --> 00:48:10.710
water. The water was polluted. There was

00:48:10.720 --> 00:48:13.349
no way to get clean water. It was wormwood. Remember, think

00:48:13.359 --> 00:48:14.390
about what the Bible talks about

00:48:14.400 --> 00:48:16.710
wormwood. The water was bad. You

00:48:16.710 --> 00:48:16.720
couldn't

00:48:16.720 --> 00:48:18.630
drink the water; the water was making

00:48:18.640 --> 00:48:20.150
people sick. So you couldn't drink

00:48:20.160 --> 00:48:22.549
purified water; there was no way to get

00:48:22.549 --> 00:48:22.559
purifying

00:48:22.559 --> 00:48:25.349
tablets. And if you had a fire,

00:48:25.359 --> 00:48:27.270
the drones would see it and they

00:48:27.280 --> 00:48:28.549
would find you, and then they

00:48:28.559 --> 00:48:29.910
would send the authorities there and you

00:48:29.920 --> 00:48:32.230
were dead anyway.

00:48:32.240 --> 00:48:35.349
So if you don't serve Jesus now with

00:48:35.359 --> 00:48:36.470
all your heart, you're not going to

00:48:36.480 --> 00:48:39.109
serve him in the end times. All these

00:48:39.119 --> 00:48:40.309
people say, 'Well, I don't believe in

00:48:40.319 --> 00:48:43.349
the rapture.'You better.

00:48:43.359 --> 00:48:47.430
You better. That's all I've got to say.

00:48:47.440 --> 00:48:49.589
You better. All these people saying, 'Well,

00:48:49.599 --> 00:48:50.470
we're going to live. We're going to be

00:48:50.480 --> 00:48:52.470
just fine. Christians are going

00:48:52.470 --> 00:48:52.480
to...'No,

00:48:52.480 --> 00:48:55.270
they're going to die.

00:48:55.280 --> 00:48:56.950
They're going to die. Not that death

00:48:56.950 --> 00:48:56.960
is

00:48:56.960 --> 00:48:59.030
a bad thing, but I'm telling you

00:48:59.040 --> 00:49:00.950
this: I don't want nobody cutting my

00:49:00.960 --> 00:49:03.030
head off. And I don't want nobody

00:49:03.040 --> 00:49:05.349
cutting my kids'heads off. I mean,

00:49:05.359 --> 00:49:07.510
seriously, that's why I said

00:49:07.520 --> 00:49:08.870
people have no comprehension of what's

00:49:08.880 --> 00:49:11.589
about to happen. And that's just part,

00:49:11.599 --> 00:49:14.630
that's just a little bitty bit of it there.

00:49:14.640 --> 00:49:18.309
It's literal hell on earth

00:49:18.319 --> 00:49:21.589
with weather events and earthquakes and

00:49:21.599 --> 00:49:26.549
volcanoes and you name

00:49:26.549 --> 00:49:26.559
it—wars,

00:49:26.559 --> 00:49:29.829
pestilence, viruses,

00:49:29.839 --> 00:49:33.430
no medical care, hiding in the woods

00:49:33.440 --> 00:49:35.109
trying to keep your life. And that's the

00:49:35.119 --> 00:49:40.230
way it was. It was awful.

00:49:40.240 --> 00:49:42.470
Like I said, I'll never forget it. And

00:49:42.470 --> 00:49:42.480
that's

00:49:42.480 --> 00:49:45.829
why I'm so vocal and so bold about

00:49:45.839 --> 00:49:48.870
what I tell you.

00:49:48.880 --> 00:49:50.069
That's why I believe the Lord

00:49:50.079 --> 00:49:52.069
showed me this. My first major event I've had

00:49:52.079 --> 00:49:54.870
with the Father.

00:49:54.880 --> 00:49:55.910
Diana said, 'You know what's

00:49:55.920 --> 00:49:57.589
interesting? Your first major event you

00:49:57.599 --> 00:49:59.430
ever had with him was something about

00:49:59.440 --> 00:50:01.510
the end times.'And we're still talking

00:50:01.520 --> 00:50:03.670
about it all these days

00:50:03.680 --> 00:50:06.950
later. It's going on

00:50:06.950 --> 00:50:06.960
years—10

00:50:06.960 --> 00:50:09.510
years, 11 years—warning people to get

00:50:09.520 --> 00:50:11.510
right with Jesus. And that's my whole

00:50:11.520 --> 00:50:13.270
mission, I feel like, is to pray about

00:50:13.280 --> 00:50:15.190
the end times. And I'm not an

00:50:15.190 --> 00:50:15.200
end-time

00:50:15.200 --> 00:50:16.710
teacher. I don't know the Bible like the

00:50:16.720 --> 00:50:19.190
scholars like Perry Stone and them, or

00:50:19.200 --> 00:50:21.430
Jonathan Cahn or whatever. Those

00:50:21.440 --> 00:50:23.430
people are real educated. I barely have

00:50:23.440 --> 00:50:25.829
a high school education.

00:50:25.839 --> 00:50:28.150
And whenever people say, 'Well, I'll

00:50:28.160 --> 00:50:30.150
never get the mark, and I'll

00:50:30.160 --> 00:50:32.390
just get my head chopped off,'I don't

00:50:32.400 --> 00:50:34.790
think they realize because we're used to

00:50:34.800 --> 00:50:36.710
having the Holy Ghost.

00:50:36.720 --> 00:50:39.829
And whenever you approach... there's been

00:50:39.839 --> 00:50:42.069
times like when I've given birth, one

00:50:42.079 --> 00:50:45.510
time I felt I was losing a lot of blood

00:50:45.520 --> 00:50:50.230
and I approached death and I almost died,

00:50:50.240 --> 00:50:53.430
and there is a peace that comes from the

00:50:53.440 --> 00:50:58.150
Holy Ghost. And I cannot even imagine

00:50:58.160 --> 00:51:00.309
approaching death without that peace

00:51:00.319 --> 00:51:02.390
that the Holy Ghost brings.

00:51:02.400 --> 00:51:05.750
So it's easy to say it now, but I

00:51:05.760 --> 00:51:09.750
cannot imagine putting my life out

00:51:09.760 --> 00:51:11.670
there without that peace. I don't want

00:51:11.680 --> 00:51:13.190
to live one second without the Holy

00:51:13.200 --> 00:51:14.710
Ghost. Just like Kathryn

00:51:14.710 --> 00:51:14.720
Kuhlman

00:51:14.720 --> 00:51:17.109
always says, 'I don't want to live one

00:51:17.119 --> 00:51:19.109
second without

00:51:19.109 --> 00:51:19.119
Him.'Yes.

00:51:19.119 --> 00:51:22.710
People have no idea. And when you

00:51:22.720 --> 00:51:25.430
don't feel that blessed

00:51:25.430 --> 00:51:25.440
assurance—you

00:51:25.440 --> 00:51:28.470
know, 'Blessed assurance, Jesus is

00:51:28.470 --> 00:51:28.480
mine'—when

00:51:28.480 --> 00:51:33.109
that's not there,

00:51:33.119 --> 00:51:37.270
it is a void. That peace that

00:51:37.280 --> 00:51:40.950
passes understanding is gone. I saw how

00:51:40.960 --> 00:51:43.829
they acted, and it was

00:51:43.839 --> 00:51:46.069
unlike any atmosphere you could ever... I

00:51:46.079 --> 00:51:48.710
felt it. I was allowed to feel what they

00:51:48.720 --> 00:51:51.990
felt. The Lord allowed me to feel it.

00:51:52.000 --> 00:51:55.750
And it's void of Him. It's void of

00:51:55.760 --> 00:51:57.750
the presence of God in the tribulation.

00:51:57.760 --> 00:51:59.030
There's nothing in people. Well, 'There's

00:51:59.040 --> 00:52:00.390
a great revival that's going to take

00:52:00.390 --> 00:52:00.400
place.'I

00:52:00.400 --> 00:52:02.790
did not see a great revival. I

00:52:02.800 --> 00:52:04.870
saw people mad and fleeing as much as

00:52:04.880 --> 00:52:08.390
they could. And they were like furious

00:52:08.400 --> 00:52:12.150
because they were still here.

00:52:12.160 --> 00:52:13.990
I don't know about you, I'm just

00:52:14.000 --> 00:52:15.430
telling y'all what I saw and what I

00:52:15.440 --> 00:52:17.510
felt. And I'm telling you, people

00:52:17.510 --> 00:52:17.520
say,

00:52:17.520 --> 00:52:19.030
'Well, this is what the scripture

00:52:19.030 --> 00:52:19.040
says.'I'm

00:52:19.040 --> 00:52:21.349
not arguing scripture

00:52:21.359 --> 00:52:23.910
with you. There

00:52:23.910 --> 00:52:23.920
are

00:52:23.920 --> 00:52:25.510
people who believe in the tribulation, there

00:52:25.510 --> 00:52:25.520
are

00:52:25.520 --> 00:52:27.109
people who don't. I'm one

00:52:27.119 --> 00:52:29.670
that

00:52:29.670 --> 00:52:29.680
doesn't.

00:52:29.680 --> 00:52:31.190
I don't believe we're appointed

00:52:31.190 --> 00:52:31.200
unto

00:52:31.200 --> 00:52:33.030
wrath.

00:52:33.040 --> 00:52:34.950
I saw the body of Christ—the ones that

00:52:34.960 --> 00:52:37.349
were right, they shot up like

00:52:37.359 --> 00:52:40.950
rockets. They're gone. In a moment, a

00:52:40.960 --> 00:52:42.549
twinkling of an eye, we were all

00:52:42.559 --> 00:52:45.990
changed. It was that fast,

00:52:46.000 --> 00:52:48.309
so much so that it created a thunderous

00:52:48.319 --> 00:52:51.510
lightning sound when it happened. And

00:52:51.520 --> 00:52:55.270
everybody heard it.

00:52:55.280 --> 00:52:56.710
It sounded like

00:52:56.720 --> 00:53:01.190
a sonic boom,

00:53:01.200 --> 00:53:03.109
and lightning bolts were going, and the

00:53:03.119 --> 00:53:05.829
sky was alive, and it was all lightning.

00:53:05.839 --> 00:53:08.630
I remember seeing it. It was

00:53:08.640 --> 00:53:11.750
amazing. But all the kids from

00:53:11.750 --> 00:53:11.760
fifteen

00:53:11.760 --> 00:53:14.309
and younger were all gone. And those

00:53:14.309 --> 00:53:14.319
mothers—I'll

00:53:14.319 --> 00:53:15.990
never forget all those

00:53:15.990 --> 00:53:16.000
mothers—'Where's

00:53:16.000 --> 00:53:17.829
my baby?'And they were

00:53:17.839 --> 00:53:20.470
freaking out trying to find their kids

00:53:20.480 --> 00:53:23.030
because they were all gone.

00:53:23.040 --> 00:53:24.549
They all got sucked up in the rapture.

00:53:24.559 --> 00:53:26.790
They weren't appointed unto wrath. And

00:53:26.800 --> 00:53:28.470
the moms were freaking out trying to

00:53:28.480 --> 00:53:29.589
find their newborns.

00:53:29.599 --> 00:53:31.109
And that's why the Bible says, 'Woe to

00:53:31.119 --> 00:53:32.390
them who have

00:53:32.390 --> 00:53:32.400
babies,'because

00:53:32.400 --> 00:53:34.470
if they had a

00:53:34.480 --> 00:53:36.630
baby during the tribulation, it was

00:53:36.640 --> 00:53:38.790
awful because those kids suffered

00:53:38.800 --> 00:53:41.430
greatly. But if they were born before

00:53:41.440 --> 00:53:43.750
the tribulation, they were taken,

00:53:43.760 --> 00:53:45.910
and they were in the rapture. And I

00:53:45.920 --> 00:53:48.069
watched the mothers searching

00:53:48.079 --> 00:53:49.750
around, and it was all on—you know how

00:53:49.760 --> 00:53:52.390
you have missing pictures of everybody.

00:53:52.400 --> 00:53:54.549
Those missing things were on the

00:53:54.559 --> 00:53:56.309
TV,

00:53:56.309 --> 00:53:56.319
with

00:53:56.319 --> 00:53:59.030
people trying to

00:53:59.040 --> 00:54:01.589
find missing

00:54:01.599 --> 00:54:02.790
children.

00:54:02.800 --> 00:54:05.910
I'm remembering more right now. And

00:54:05.920 --> 00:54:07.750
I'm telling you, there are things I forgot,

00:54:07.760 --> 00:54:11.030
but I just saw

00:54:11.030 --> 00:54:11.040
it—the

00:54:11.040 --> 00:54:13.990
missing faces on the pictures

00:54:14.000 --> 00:54:15.270
like they used to put on the milk

00:54:15.280 --> 00:54:17.109
cartons in the old days.

00:54:17.119 --> 00:54:19.109
I don't know why that just

00:54:19.109 --> 00:54:19.119
flashed

00:54:19.119 --> 00:54:24.230
back at me.

00:54:24.240 --> 00:54:25.990
You know, there are little pieces that

00:54:26.000 --> 00:54:29.109
I'll forget, and then whenever I

00:54:29.119 --> 00:54:31.109
go, I'll remember it and it comes back

